com.cleo.lexicom.external

Interface ILicense

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote

    public interface ILicense
extends java.rmi.Remote
    Establishes an interface to VersaLex's License. Refer to ILexiCom.getLicense().

    Methods provided allow for retrieval of installation's license information.

      • getActiveProtocolCount

        long[] getActiveProtocolCount(com.cleo.lexicom.beans.LicenseFields.Protocol protocol)
                       throws java.lang.Exception
        Get the number of active hosts or mailboxes for each protocol. If isMailboxLimitPerHost() is true, then hosts per protocol is returned. If isMailboxLimitPerHost() is false, then mailboxes per protocol is returned.
        Parameters:
        protocol - The protocol for which to get the active counts
        Returns:
        The number of hosts or mailboxes for the protocol int[0]=Number of non-LDAP hosts or mailboxes for the protocol int[1]=Number of LDAP users for the protocol
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception
